<h1>Alish Uprety  "Zoos to be Seen"</h1>
  <p class= "footer">Created By: Alish Uprety On 3/23/2019</p>

<p1 class="one">Zoos are living museum which are opened with the purpose to conserve the animals. In the United States, zoos are visited by over 180 million people anually. Animals have good life in zoos because they do have plently of food and water, so that they sho uldn't starve of hunger. Animals are not for ours use of entertainment so there are many things and precautions that neeeds to be taken by people while visitng the zoos.There are plenty of benefits of maintaining zoos for both animals and people.</p1>
<br></br>

<h2>Here are some of the zoos of Boston and USA</h2>
<ol>
<li><a href="https://www.zoonewengland.org/franklin-park-zoo">Franklin Park Zoo</li></a>
<li><a href="https://capronparkzoo.com/">Capron Park Zoo</li></a>
<li><a href="https://www.rwpzoo.org/">Roger Williams Park Zoo</li></a>
<li><a href="">Columbus Zoo and Aquarium</li></a>
<li><a href="https://www.midohiofoodbank.org">Brookfield Zoo</li></a>
</ol>
<br></br>
<p2 class="two"> There are many endangered animals in today's world. If zoos are well managed then, it helps to protect or fight against wildlife extinction. Franklin Park Zoo is a great zoo placed in the bostoon city for easy acess to public.<img class ="six" src="images/elephant.jpg"alt="Elephant Picture">Zoo also helps people to see different animals and know about the animals and know about the animals that they have never heard of before. Similarly, zoos helps people to learn about the importance of nature.</p2>
<br></br>
<p3 class="three"> Zoos bring human beings closer to wildlife. It also can be economic resource for a community. The Smithsonian National Zoo is one of many that are working with local college and universities to create a degree program. Moreover, in zoos animals are compelled to live in the small area which hampered their development and growth.<img class ="six" src="images/cheetah.jpg" alt="Cheetah Picture"> Therefore, if the zoos is maintained and enoufh space is provided to the animals then they can enjoy their life and feels the freedom due to which they be happy and makes other hapapy as well. </p3>